Class EventDatabaseRepresentation

java.lang.Object
com.example.eventscan.Database.EventDatabaseRepresentation
public class EventDatabaseRepresentation extends Object
The representation of an Event inside the database Currently stripping out the list of attendees as well as the organizer objects and replace them with just their UIDs
